rows.label: qev041408_MSG0001
rows.name:
Hmm. Expression of friend seems troubled.
Anything Mujiji can do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0002
rows.name:
It is job of brother to help out in times of trouble.
Go on! Spill guts to Mujiji![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Mujiji about the caravan's business.

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0003
rows.name:
Oh, little of this and that. Skinning animals for pelts...
Selling their meat... Sneaking off with weapons of
Ganglion and reselling them...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0004
rows.name:
Anything dangerous and profitable, really.
Nopon of this caravan are wild and fearless outlaws![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0009
rows.name:
...Oh, okay. Least Mujiji can do is give Nan big,
colorful send-off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0011
rows.name:
Take this contract and wait for massive fireworks.
Mujiji never do anything in half-measures![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0012
rows.name:
Mujiji rough and tumble Nopon for sure.
Anyone Mujiji not like gets smacked around![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0013
rows.name:
...Mujiji actually plan on beating down that perv at
some point, but if number of Elder Nan coming up,
Mujiji let it slide.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041408_MSG0014
rows.name:
Caravan of Mujiji will create fireworks show from
heck to light way there for old geezer![ST:wait ]
